---
import { SERIES_START, SERIES_END } from "../lib/series";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-ink-900 bg-paper mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-10">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-editorial-wide pb-8 border-b border-ink-300">
      <div class="max-w-prose">
        <p class="kicker text-ink-500 mb-2">COLOPHON</p>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl leading-snug text-ink-900 mb-3">
          Leaves.PH is an open, reproducible measurement series of Metro Manila tree cover.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
          Independent. Not affiliated with any government agency, NGO, or LGU. Inputs are public-record satellite imagery and open datasets. Code MIT, data CC-BY-4.0. The published value is a methodology-specific measurement; particular allegations of unpermitted cutting require independent investigation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-ink-700 space-y-3">
        <div>
          <p class="text-ink-500">REPORT</p>
          <p><a href="/methodology" class="no-underline text-ink-900">methodology</a></p>
          <p><a href="/data" class="no-underline text-ink-900">data downloads</a></p>
          <p><a href="/faq" class="no-underline text-ink-900">faq</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-ink-500">CONTACT</p>
          <p><a href="https://github.com/xmpuspus/leaves-ph/issues" class="no-underline text-ink-900">submit a correction</a></p>
          <p><a href="https://github.com/xmpuspus/leaves-ph/security/advisories/new" class="no-underline text-ink-900">private security advisory</a></p>
          <p><a href="/privacy" class="no-underline text-ink-900">privacy &amp; takedown</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-6 text-xs text-ink-500 font-mono leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        IMAGERY: modified Copernicus Sentinel data {SERIES_START}-{SERIES_END} (ESA). LOSS LAYER: Hansen et al. 2013 via UMD GLAD / Global Forest Watch. LAND COVER: ESA WorldCover v200 (CC-BY-4.0), Google Dynamic World v1. CANOPY HEIGHT: Meta AI / Land &amp; Carbon Lab Global Canopy Height v2 (CC-BY-4.0). BOUNDARIES: OpenStreetMap contributors (ODbL), Philippine Statistics Authority.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        &copy; {year} LEAVES.PH. CITE: Leaves.PH (2026), Sentinel-2 2019-2026 (2026 provisional), https://github.com/xmpuspus/leaves-ph
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
